{"tid":56243,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不定時直播]由香港踩單車上廣州","createTime":"2016-12-27T05:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T15:28:26.000Z","uid":67976,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf8289be82975d7c6ccf91bb7d262968ab00fe7","tid":56243,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"其實想踩單車旅行好耐，只係一直都無時間同心力。適逢sem迫，又有感情問題，唔想喪飲酒咁頹，把心一橫就決定踩單車避節，上年去伊朗都係咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n本身老母唔知我踩單車返大陸，我話去露營好幾日就過左骨，hehe。之後放左架單車起朋友屋企，費事佢問長問短啦。<br />\n<br />\n今朝去完朋友屋企拎車就出發，諗住大窩口踩去上水再轉火車過關。查實我無乜點踩過公路，最多都係踩去下白泥，真係唔知那兒來的勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝踩到唔記得食野，一記得食野就去左大埔醫肚，hea到打完呢篇野為止。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0wyuzps4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0wyuzps4&h=f2a84a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個show me your love飯都真係幾難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家應該出左大埔入上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌打呢篇野用左好撚多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夜晚得閒再打返多啲"},{"pid":"245db83107c9f866abe9c71a4d31c746e05fe76f","tid":56243,"uid":7880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"lm，有想過行路上廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fad3be39919506a19364776b202fd92830e434","tid":56243,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"係落馬州過？"},{"pid":"221bafd055e43446a10dca5a142214c88e7df6ad","tid":56243,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm，有想過行路上廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行路我諗要差唔多一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d715e56a527b1aeaad27dd13a6bb4537992b07